Tipsy autorickshawdriver slits his throatN. Zaheer Hussain(32), an autorickshaw driver, reportedly slit his throat with a broken piece of bottle after the police caught him for driving under the influence of alcohol on Friday.The auto driver hailed from Kamarajapuram near R.S. Puram.He was taking a passenger in his vehicle whenhe was stopped by the police near Chinthamani Junction. Realising that he would be penalised, Hussain slit his throat with a broken piece of bottle and suffered injuries, police said.A case has been registered.